#include <stdio.h>
#include <iostream>
#include <set>
#include <queue>
#include <algorithm>

using namespace std;

#define DEBUG 0

int main(){

	//freopen("in","r",stdin);
	
	priority_queue <int> pq;
	int N;
	scanf("%d",&N);
	int K;
	scanf("%d",&K);
	for(int tt=0;tt<K;tt++){
		int x;
		scanf("%d",&x);
		pq.push(x);
	}

	for(int tt=0;tt<N-K;tt++){
		int x;
		scanf("%d",&x);
		if(x!=-1){
			if(x < pq.top()){
				pq.pop();
				pq.push(x);
			}
		}
		else
			printf("%d\n", pq.top());
	}
	return 0;

}
